    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.21.74" />
                <fw type="curatorial">74</fw>
                
            <fw type="letterhead">    
                <hi rend="caps">SKYRIM FARM</hi>
              <lb/> 
                <hi rend="caps">ROUTE 7</hi>
              <lb/>  
                <hi rend="caps">COLUMBIA, MISSOURI</hi>
            </fw>
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>5-5-'58</dateline>
                
                
                
                <salute>Dear Friends:</salute>
                </opener>
                
                <p>I've decided to fly all the way to Ithaca. Will leave here on the 18th or 19th, and will let you know the exact date later. I will not bring sorrow into your home. We will have a spot of that fine old Scotch you mentioned, and the three of us will talk about what we know is good and beautiful.</p>
                
                <closer>
                <salute>Love to both</salute>
                <signed>Jno. N.</signed> 
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
